}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Summary judgment is proper when the \u8220\'3fmovant shows that there is no genuine dispute as to any material fact and the movant is entitled to judgment as a matter of law.\u8221\'3f 
}
