Defendant\rquote s Response included a Declaration of Jenisa Story, which identifies Ms. Story as Defendant\rquote s Chief Operating Officer, asserts factual knowledge related to the case, and includes twelve exhibits. (Story Decl., Exs. A-L.) The facts asserted in Defendant\rquote s Response rely extensively on the Story Declaration and its accompanying exhibits.
\par 
