*1225
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 representation. (Crain Decl., Ex. 14 at 16-17.) The fact that Ms. Whittaker asked for documentation, albeit not in writing, is further indication that HASCO understood Plaintiff was asserting her rights under VAWA. Additionally, Plaintiff represented her status to HASCO on at least two other occasions. (
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
